# 🔥 Interview Questions

### 1. Difference between int and Integer?

👉 int = primitive
👉 Integer = object (wrapper class)

---

### 2. Where are variables stored?

👉 Stack (primitive), Heap (objects)

---

### 3. What is type casting?

👉 Converting one type to another

---

### 4. Why String is non-primitive?

👉 Because it is a class (object)

